Package ojc.bain.synapse

Contains classes that implement synapse models.

See: Description

Package ojc.bain.synapse Description

Contains classes that implement synapse models. All synapse models extend from SynapseCollection Synapse models are divided into those designed for rate-based encodings and spike-timing-based encodings, in the packages ojc.bain.synapse.rate and ojc.bain.synapse.spiking respectively.
